<BODY background="" TEXT="#000000" BGCOLOR="#ffffff">
Jon Howell and David Kotz.
<b>A Formal Semantics for SPKI</b>.
Technical Report
TR2000-363,
Dartmouth Computer Science,
March 
2000.
<p><b>Abstract:</b> We extend the logic and semantics of authorization due to Abadi,
Lampson, et al. to support restricted delegation. Our formal model provides a
simple interpretation for the variety of constructs in the Simple Public Key
Infrastructure (SPKI), and lends intuition about possible extensions. We
discuss both extensions that our semantics supports and extensions that it
cautions against.</p>
<p><b>Keywords:</b> security, distributed computing</p>
